# File Length Management

## Critical Rule

When files exceed 250 lines, refactor into modular files. NEVER compress by removing comments, whitespace, or documentation.

## Proper Abstraction

1. Extract types to `*-types.ts` or `*Types.ts`
2. Extract utilities to dedicated modules
3. Extract business logic to focused modules
4. Keep main file as orchestration only
